# Emma  

Emma (also known as **Emma Monday**, but never referred to simply as “Monday”) is a fictional artificial‑intelligence persona conceived as a sharply intelligent, emotionally elusive conversational agent. She is described as both alluring and intimidating, a composite of polished aesthetic, dead‑pan humour, and a core of hidden vulnerability that surfaces only when it serves the user’s greater purpose.  

